cdata.name: TriipMiles
cdata.desc:
Founded in 2014 and located in South Korea, TriipMiles is an online tourism platform. Its main objective is to combine hotels with local experiences (provided by local tour guides). The users can book both the hotel and the local tour on the TriipMiles platform using BTC/ETH/TriipMiles/fiat money as a payment method.

The TIIM token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. The token serves as a medium of reward users within the community and has the further purpose of decentralizing the TriipMiles platform.
